  "detailed_description": "<h1>Remote Play Together Info</h1><p><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/819940/extras/716b75a55b8738e3a60cee33e119df55.avif?t=1616541472\" width=800 height=80 /></span><br>The setup for Remote Play Together is exactly the same you would do in one PC. In case that you run into problems follow this list:<br><br>1) Disconnect all the XBOX gamepads from all the PCs<br>2) Connect one by one the gamepads again (Every player should now have input)<br>3) Use the \"Play Couch\" mode.<br>4) There are some cases that player 2 can control multiple selections, don't worry about that. In the match every player should be able to control their ship.<br>5) Have fun!</p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/819940/extras/0f3f3bca5f4d3e4a14b253c92f368329.avif?t=1616541472\" width=600 height=192 /></span><br>We could write lots of nice and carefully placed things about the lore and stuff. But come on, this game is all about PURE! FAST PACED MAYHEM!<br><br>Destroy everyone in the name of RUM!  <br><br><strong>These are the skills that will lead you to VICTORY!</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/819940/extras/b510d4510344cad6e4888e697d6ac60f.avif?t=1616541472\" width=600 height=192 /></span><br>Our signature skill, the skill that started it all!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/819940/extras/8b2a34184f706693cf01132ab2e89ff4.poster.avif?t=1616541472\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/819940/extras/8b2a34184f706693cf01132ab2e89ff4.webm?t=1616541472\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/819940/extras/8b2a34184f706693cf01132ab2e89ff4.mp4?t=1616541472\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/819940/extras/973677d4f5ca81e75b5bb8a6f389e1ea.avif?t=1616541472\" width=600 height=192 /></span><br>After Ramming other ships we said, well..what kind of old-school ships don't have Cannon Balls!?<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/819940/extras/0ce2626b162b550eb76c1e5fb658187f.poster.avif?t=1616541472\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/819940/extras/0ce2626b162b550eb76c1e5fb658187f.webm?t=1616541472\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/819940/extras/0ce2626b162b550eb76c1e5fb658187f.mp4?t=1616541472\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/819940/extras/b54be7381be1a0399e01568adfa157f2.avif?t=1616541472\" width=600 height=192 /></span><br>Is someone tailing you? Give em your Mine as a present! They will LOVE IT!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/819940/extras/7eab43b8345a32e7ae9904b31a3b6c56.poster.avif?t=1616541472\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/819940/extras/7eab43b8345a32e7ae9904b31a3b6c56.webm?t=1616541472\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/819940/extras/7eab43b8345a32e7ae9904b31a3b6c56.mp4?t=1616541472\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/819940/extras/8369f780ac17e7dce04541cb370b7120.avif?t=1616541472\" width=600 height=192 /></span><br>We know it was needed.. so we delivered! Now you can mock your enemies all you want even in game!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/819940/extras/52348c9e1e8d706357feb3d5df6703d6.poster.avif?t=1616541472\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/819940/extras/52348c9e1e8d706357feb3d5df6703d6.webm?t=1616541472\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/819940/extras/52348c9e1e8d706357feb3d5df6703d6.mp4?t=1616541472\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
